VERKADA_API_KEY=This should be your API Key==
ELASTIC_PASSWORD=At least six characters long
KIBANA_SYSTEM_PASSWORD=At least six characters long and you will need to set in Kibana refer to README
KIBANA_ENCRYPTION_KEY=Create Key using command "openssl rand -base64 32" in linux or wsl==
AZURE_TENANT_ID=Directory (tenant) ID from your Microsoft Entra app registration
AZURE_CLIENT_ID=Application (client) ID from your Microsoft Entra app registration
AZURE_CERT_PATH=Path to the PEM file holding the private key + certificate uploaded to the app registration
WINDOWS_IP=This is the IP for your device